slide.p:
This tutorial will walk you through setting up some user roles
        for the diner webapp. This will involve enabling sessions,
        and is a great excuse for integrating the "Caboose" package.

pre.code:
function render() {
    ...

    // integrate any needed CSS framework & components
    $this->data['caboose_styles'] = $this->caboose->styles();
    $this->data['caboose_scripts'] = $this->caboose->scripts();
    $this->data['caboose_trailings'] = $this->caboose->trailings();

    $this->parser->parse('_template', $this->data);
}

